race.comment: I LOVE YOUR SMILE (2) was in good form prior to tackling the Listed Kalgoorlie Cup where she was just outclassed. Better suited back to this grade today where she won her two starts prior. Pike rides again this time and she's expected to be storming home late in the race. LOMBADINA (7) finished 0.7L off the winner last start at Ascot and finished behind I LOVE YOUR SMILE the two prior to that. May need some luck getting off the fence from the inside barrier, but she drops in weight for CJP and has to be included on recent efforts. ANTIQUE STAR (4) finished 0.4L off the winner last start and was narrowly beaten the start prior too. Racing in top order and this looks to set up nicely for her. LYRICAL ANGEL (10) is better than she showed last time out and can bounce back to her best form. RYEWOOD (3) has been going around in good company this time in work. Not to be discounted back in grade.
